data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath house sits on two lots in Kiroli Woods Subdivision.  The large room at the back of the house has double french doors overlooking the back yard.  This room could be used as a Main Bedroom, gaming room, bonus living area, the possibles are limitless. There is a two car carport.  This house has been very well maintained and is very spacious inside and out.  The roof has been replaced about 2 years ago, part of the yard has been fenced in within the last year, Plumbing in both bath rooms has recently been updated, A/C unit recently serviced. Convenient to stores, hospitals, Doctors, schools and Kiroli Park.
